name: Attack of the Jam filled baby
name_original: Attack of the Jam filled baby
description:
Un-bugged version here:

https://dj990j.itch.io/attack-of-the-jam-filled-baby-unbugged

This game will be updated when voting is done!!

Tonya has been asked to watch her nephew but something weird starts to happen. Can you find a way out of this mess? Play through this short RPG Maker MV game in less than 30 minutes.

This will be my very first RPG Maker game I've completed in the 10+ years of my tinkering! :D

This game was made for "Build your own game jam by Drifty and Tea" https://itch.io/jam/build-your-own-game-jam. The themes I used for this project are Purple, Not what it seems, Babies, and Time Travel.

  • A lot of numbers to remember
  • I don't know about that jam in the frig.
  • What's that book on the table?
  • Outside is scary in the dark
  • Dryer first?

Hello my name is Jasmine (DJ990J) and I make games as a hobby.
